mas-New Year festive lunch. Bookings at 22298947.				 																																	 Till January 11 at Pakwan, 70B Purna Das Road, -3476/ 8101: Kool Kebabs  an array of exciting varities of kebabs.				 																LECTURE-DEMONSTRATION				 																																	 December 29 at Oxford Bookstore, 17 Park Street; 7 pm: Oxford Bookstore presents Pandit Chitresh Das and the Chitresh Das Dance Company, USA in a lecture, demonstration and discussion theme, Preserving Indian tradition abroad and creating a cultural bridge between India and America.				 																																	 January 4 at Sandre Hall; 6.30 pm: The Calcutta School of Music presents a lecture-demonstration by Indian-born Clarence Barlow (who now resides in Germany) on The Raslila Festival in Berlin 2003 as a forum of India-born avant garde composer resident in the Western World.				 																xmas special				 																																	 Till December 30 at Lions Club Childrens Corner, Deshapriya Park: Vibgyor hosts camp for children during Christmas holidays. Details: 9831260807/ 9831234659.				 																																	 Till January 1 at FunCity; 10 am - 8 pm: Winter Carnival features live band, dance performance, magic show, various contest, food, etc.				 																BEAUTY				 																																	 Till January 1 at 3A Gurusaday Road; 8 am - 8 pm: Head Turners, in collaboration with LOreal, offers makeup tips, mehendi, body tattoo, skin care and aroma therapy consultation, and hairdo complimenting winter clothes.				 																WORKSHOP				 																																	 December 29 - January 3 at Bharatiyam Cultural Multiplex, IB 201 Salt Lake, 10 am - 5 pm: EZCC holds a workshop on Bharata Natyam to be conducted by Smt. A. Vadivudevi, well-known dancer, choreographer and teacher from Thanjavur. Call to register.
